modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds a rotating [bridge](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-bridges/) that users can place. Dancapo suggested it so Guppycur whipped it up real quick like.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Rotating_Bridge)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
